data.value: 1. Place eight queens on a chessboard so that no two queens attack each other. 2. Ensure queens are positioned so they do not share the same row, column, or diagonal. 3. Use the "Solve" button for an automatic solution to the puzzle. 4. Alternatively, manually place the queens by selecting squares on the board. 5. Warning message will pop-up if there is invalid move detected.
